{"id":232963122,"title":"備用帽問題？","content":"目前有一頂主力的Z-7素色帽通勤用\n然後有一頂備用的ZS-811\n如果要載人也是用備用帽給後座使用\n\n只是最近幾次載人都很不愉快\n要馬對方不想戴\n不然就是被嫌麻煩\n甚至說直接不戴安全帽罰單她出…\n還差點在路上吵起來\n\n感覺大家對全罩式安全帽接受度不太高…\n所以想再買一頂備用帽\n只用來載人\n但是希望是「多數人能接受」的帽子\n所以想選3/4的帽子\n預算不太高2~3k\n\n目前看上的只有\n\nRUFU RU168\nhttps://i.imgur.com/OUt3Z2w.jpg\n\n\n這頂會容易讓別人不想戴或嫌麻煩嗎？\n有其他推薦的嗎？(安全性不要太低的3/4)\n\n謝謝","excerpt":"目前有一頂主力的Z-7素色帽通勤用，然後有一頂備用的ZS-811，如果要載人也是用備用帽給後座使用，只是最近幾次載人都很不愉快，要馬對方不想戴，不然就是被嫌麻煩，甚至說直接不戴安全帽罰單她出…，還差點","anonymousSchool":false,"anonymousDepartment":true,"pinned":false,"forumId":"d208d1e2-6f14-429b-97b7-75a2dd4f761c","replyId":null,"createdAt":"2020-01-26T16:39:07.651Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-26T16:54:33.604Z","commentCount":33,"likeCount":28,"tags":[],"topics":[],"supportedReactions":null,"withNickname":false,"reportReason":"","hiddenByAuthor":false,"meta":{"layout":"classic"},"forumName":"汽機車","forumAlias":"vehicle","school":"國立臺東大學","replyTitle":null,"gender":"F","personaSubscriptable":false,"reactions":[{"id":"286f599c-f86a-4932-82f0-f5a06f1eca03","count":28}],"hidden":false,"customStyle":null,"isSuspiciousAccount":false,"layout":"classic","withImages":true,"withVideos":false,"media":[{"url":"https://i.imgur.com/OUt3Z2w.jpg"}],"reportReasonText":"","mediaMeta":[{"id":"d6e873ba-f03d-4169-ba8d-21a486fcf5cb","url":"https://i.imgur.com/OUt3Z2wl.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://i.imgur.com/OUt3Z2wl.jpg","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/OUt3Z2wl.jpg","type":"image/thumbnail","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-26T16:54:33.604Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-26T16:54:33.604Z"},{"id":"d6e873ba-f03d-4169-ba8d-21a486fcf5cb","url":"https://i.imgur.com/OUt3Z2w.jpg","normalizedUrl":"https://imgur.com/OUt3Z2w","thumbnail":"https://i.imgur.com/OUt3Z2wl.jpg","type":"image/imgur","tags":["ANNOTATED"],"createdAt":"2020-01-26T16:54:33.604Z","updatedAt":"2020-01-26T16:54:33.604Z"}],"postAvatar":""}